task.summary: Introduced GeneratedColorProducer, to track what object is responsible for an element of the color pipeline. This might be a shader, a surface, a texture, etc.
More expansion of the economics package, including support for grouping Expenses into an ExpenseRange.
ExpenseData can now produce an ExpenseRange of a specific interval.
Scalar implements Comparable. Fixed a bug in ExpenseRange add method.
Introduced ETH currency type, minor changes to ExpenseRange and Atomic, and removed UpdateListener (Temporal should be used in its place).
Migrated some animation functionality from the Explorer Simulation to Common Animation. Simulation is now a subclass of Animation.
Migrated a lot of functionality from PhotonField into Common.
Migrated Matrix3D and Matrix3DSolutionOutput into Common.
Working with legacy jogl data structures until we migrate everything in Explorer to our own structures.
Introduced normalize method and set method.
Introduced getters for x,y,z,w in Rotf.
w is actually q0, not q3. Also, introduced inverse method.
Introduced set method for Rotf in Mat3f.
Introduced load method for Resource that reads from a byte array.
Use Swing Event Thread for events listeners that are AWT components.
Introduced a sub method accepting Vector.
Introduced add method which accepts Vector.
setRow method accepts double instead of float.
Introduced set method which accepts a double instead of a float.
Some improvements to econ package. Added private member to Frequency class.
